        <dc:description xml:lang="en">This is the distribution in RDF/Turtle of the Labour and Social Policy Ministry Ontology about the citizen's social and employment record within the public information system and its function as a hub for accessing information on citizens, especially those relating to their involvement in inclusion initiatives arising from the need to address their own or their family's social and employment vulnerabilities.</dc:description>
